thread.title: Q-Free signs NOK 37 mln RUC autopass contracts in Norway
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Q-Free signs NOK 37 mln RUC autopass contracts in Norway | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Q-Free signs NOK 37 mln RUC autopass contracts in Norway
text:
Sept 11 Q-Free ASA :
* Announces Road User Charging (RUC) autopass contracts in Norway worth 37 million Norwegian crowns ($4.50 million)
* Contracts are from the Norwegian Roads Administration
* Delivery will be completed during 2016
Source text for Eikon:
 ($1 = 8.2227 Norwegian crowns) (Gdynia Newsroom)
